# Loyalty — Cron Points Expiry Trigger
# M10-S08: publishes the cron-loyalty-expiry trigger, dispatched to ExpirePointsTriggerHandler
# (M17-S03). In production, Cloud Scheduler publishes the same trigger directly to Pub/Sub daily
# at 02:00 UTC — this endpoint is the local/manual trigger path only, protected by the global
# InternalApiGuard (X-Internal-Key), not PubSubPushGuard.
# Response is { ok: true } once the trigger is published — it does not wait for the job to
# finish. Requires the Pub/Sub emulator running (pnpm infra:up).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}

### POST /cron/loyalty-expiry — publish the daily points-expiry trigger
POST {{baseUrl}}/cron/loyalty-expiry
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

###
